data.description: You do not want to miss out on this move in ready home! Its unique corner lot location and historic charm make it an ideal house for a family. Throughout the years, the house has been thoughtfully renovated, updated, and remodeled. The house features three bedrooms and two bathrooms, which make it a comfortable place to live. The renovation includes new cabinetry, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a breakfast bar. Among the amenities are a utility room, a washer/dryer, and a workshop with window air conditioning. The design of the property allows for easy access through the breezeway and French doors. Besides spacious outdoor storage closets on the carport, the backyard courtyard paver patio features a vine-covered post and decorative gates. A convenient recreational space is available just steps away from the residence at Coronado Park, which features a dog park as well. Close to shopping, dining, and schools. NEW ROOF is being installed!
